Sales Forecasting System

This is an End-to-End Machine Learning Web Application that predicts sales based on input features using a trained regression model.

Project Overview
- Objective: Build a predictive tool to estimate future sales.
- Model: Linear Regression (Saved as .pkl file).
- Interface: Interactive web dashboard built with Streamlit.
- Deployment: Hosted on Streamlit Cloud.

Tech Stack
- Language: Python
- Libraries: Scikit-learn, Pandas, NumPy, Joblib
- Web Framework: Streamlit

How to Use
1. Visit the live app here: [https://eslam-sales-forecast.streamlit.app/](https://eslam-sales-forecast.streamlit.app/)
2. Enter the Unit Price and Marketing Budget.
3. Click on Generate Prediction to see the estimated sales result.
